Description: Activity tracker agent for Ubuntu/GNOME
 Aisisstant tracks user activity across all applications and scores
 active vs passive vs idle time. Data is stored in PostgreSQL.
 .
 Features:
  - Keyboard input tracking (key count, not content) via evdev
  - Mouse tracking (distance, clicks, scroll) via evdev
  - Window focus tracking (app, tab title, duration) via AT-SPI
  - Microphone activity detection via PipeWire
  - Activity scoring algorithm (active/passive/idle per 30s)
  - PostgreSQL storage in Docker container
  - GTK4/Adwaita setup wizard and settings UI
